Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,DDE-RAG. Don't move the data. Move the compute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM federated question across Albany, Lejeune, Quantico — 70 GB of\Nsource data.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Kamiwaza-deployed inference containers, one per data node. ICD\N503 per-enclave accreditation preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Top: naive central RAG pulls 50 GB over the wire. Bottom: DDE pushes\N10 MB of compute IN, only answers come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Two thousand times less data over the wire. Seconds, not hours. DCSA\Nspillage class GREEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Federated answer composed by the Kamiwaza Model Gateway. Serial-number\NM1A1s, work-order context, TM thresholds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_DDE_NODES and the same code routes against your Inference\NMesh. Hash-chained audit per dispatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Compute-at-data, deployed in hours, not\Nmonths.
